# Patient User Styling Patterns

## File Organization

### Component-Level Styles
- Each page/component has its own `.less` file
- Import shared styles from component libraries
- Use nested selectors with BEM-like naming

### Shared Prescription Styles
- Common prescription component styles in `prescription.less`
- Import in components that use prescription patterns

```less
// ✅ GOOD - Organized by component hierarchy
.diagnosis-page {
  .diagnosis-container {
    .diagnosis-header {
      // styles
    }
  }
}
```

