### Flexbox Layouts
```less
// ✅ GOOD - Header with actions
.diagnosis-header {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

// ✅ GOOD - Two-column layout
.patient-info-wrapper {
  display: flex;
  gap: 24px;
  
  .patient-info-left {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 280px;
  }
  
  .patient-info-right {
    flex: 1;
  }
