.user-name-item {
  &.active {
    background: #f0f0f0;
  }
}

// ✅ GOOD - Checked state
.check-item {
  &.checked {
    input[type='checkbox'] {
      accent-color: #1890ff;
    }
  }
}
```

## Scrollbar Styling

### Custom Scrollbars
